<plot>Dismissed from his job as a staff manager at a furniture factory, Max finds a new job but with a low salary. Muriel, Max's mistress, thinks he should accept an offer for an employment in Australia. She and her daughter will go with him on the condition that Max divorces his wife so that he and Muriel can get married.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?012884</url></doc>
